---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

const updated = '2026-05-05';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy — Yield to Freedom"
  description="How Creative Bandit LLC collects, uses, and protects information when you use yieldtofreedom.com."
>
  <article
    class="max-w-3xl space-y-4 leading-relaxed text-slate-700 [&_a]:font-semibold [&_a]:text-blue-700 hover:[&_a]:text-blue-900 [&_strong]:font-semibold"
  >
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900">Privacy policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Last updated: {updated} (UTC)</p>
    <p>
      This policy describes how <strong>Creative Bandit LLC</strong> (“we,” “us”) handles information when you visit
      <strong>yieldtofreedom.com</strong> and related services (“Site”). By using the Site, you agree to this policy
      alongside our <a href="/terms">Terms of service</a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">What we collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
      <li>
        <strong>Email addresses</strong> you submit through newsletter or contact forms. We store them to send
        confirmations, updates, and (if you opt in) educational content. You can unsubscribe using links in those
        emails where applicable.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Technical data</strong> that servers and analytics may log automatically: approximate location (from IP),
        browser type, device type, referring URLs, and timestamps. We use this to operate, secure, and improve the Site.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Theme preference</strong> may be stored in your browser (<code class="rounded bg-slate-100 px-1">localStorage</code>) so the
        light/dark appearance persists.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      When enabled, we may use <strong>Google Analytics 4</strong> to understand aggregate traffic. GA4 can set cookies
      or use similar technologies per Google’s policies. You can control cookies through your browser and use Google’s
      opt-out tools where available.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">How we use information</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
      <li>Provide and maintain the Site, including calculators and ETF directory features.</li>
      <li>Send transactional messages (for example, subscription confirmations).</li>
      <li>Detect abuse, fraud, or technical issues.</li>
      <li>Comply with law or enforce our terms.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not sell your personal information.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Service providers</h2>
    <p>
      We rely on vendors that process data on our behalf under contractual safeguards—for example hosting (such as
      Vercel), database providers (such as Neon), email delivery (such as Resend), authentication or payments when those
      features are offered, and market-data APIs used server-side to populate ETF metrics. Those providers access only what
      they need to perform their services.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Retention</h2>
    <p>
      We keep subscriber and operational records only as long as needed for the purposes above, unless a longer period is
      required by law. You may request deletion of marketing-related records subject to verification and legal exceptions.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Security</h2>
    <p>
      We use reasonable administrative and technical safeguards appropriate to the nature of the Site. No online service
      can guarantee absolute security.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Children</h2>
    <p>The Site is not directed at children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect their personal information.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">International visitors</h2>
    <p>
      If you access the Site from outside the United States, you understand your information may be processed in the United
      States where our providers operate.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Changes</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this policy from time to time. We will revise the “Last updated” date above for material changes and,
      where appropriate, provide additional notice on the Site.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about privacy: <a href="mailto:hello@yieldtofreedom.com">hello@yieldtofreedom.com</a>
    </p>
    <p class="pt-4"><a href="/">← Back to home</a></p>
  </article>
</Base>
